1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:05,889
Just another day of staring at a tiny glowing rectangle.

2
00:00:05,889 --> 00:00:11,769
Everyone is walking somewhere important. I am not.

3
00:00:11,769 --> 00:00:17,660
The floor is shinier than my future.

4
00:00:17,660 --> 00:00:23,550
People coming, people going. Still sitting.

5
00:00:23,550 --> 00:00:29,429
Still here. Still waiting. Still staring.
